%% Planning-relaties
StapTemp -->|isStepOfPlan| Plan
StapWind -->|isStepOfPlan| Plan
StapLicht -->|isStepOfPlan| Plan
StapRegen -->|isStepOfPlan| Plan
StapAfw -->|isStepOfPlan| Plan
StapRaam -->|isStepOfPlan| Plan
StapAfw -.->|isPrecededBy| StapTemp
StapRaam -.->|isPrecededBy| StapAfw
StapRaam -.->|isPrecededBy| StapWind
StapRaam -.->|isPrecededBy| StapLicht
StapRaam -.->|isPrecededBy| StapRegen
VarTemp -->|isOutputVarOf| StapTemp
VarTemp -.->|isInputVarOf| StapAfw
VarWind -->|isOutputVarOf| StapWind
VarWind -.->|isInputVarOf| StapRaam
VarLicht -->|isOutputVarOf| StapLicht
VarLicht -.->|isInputVarOf| StapRaam
VarRegen -->|isOutputVarOf| StapRegen
VarRegen -.->|isInputVarOf| StapRaam
VarAfw -->|isOutputVarOf| StapAfw
VarAfw -.->|isInputVarOf| StapRaam
VarRaamStand -->|isOutputVarOf| StapRaam

%% Deployment-relaties
Zaal -->|isHostedBy| Gebouw
Gevel -->|isHostedBy| Gebouw
Thermo -->|isHostedBy| Zaal
RaamOpener -->|isHostedBy| Zaal
WindM -->|isHostedBy| Gevel
LichtM -->|isHostedBy| Gevel
RegenS -->|isHostedBy| Gevel
Thermo -->|implements| StapTemp
WindM -->|implements| StapWind
LichtM -->|implements| StapLicht
RegenS -->|implements| StapRegen
Besturing -->|implements| StapAfw
RaamOpener -->|implements| StapRaam

%% Execution-relaties (observations → steps)
TempObs -->|correspondsToStep| StapTemp
WindObs -->|correspondsToStep| StapWind
LichtObs -->|correspondsToStep| StapLicht
RegenObs -->|correspondsToStep| StapRegen
AfwObs -->|correspondsToStep| StapAfw
RaamAct -->|correspondsToStep| StapRaam

%% Execution-relaties (observations → sensors)
TempObs -->|madeBySensor| Thermo
WindObs -->|madeBySensor| WindM
LichtObs -->|madeBySensor| LichtM
RegenObs -->|madeBySensor| RegenS
AfwObs -->|madeBySensor| Besturing
RaamAct -->|madeByActuator| RaamOpener

%% Execution-relaties (observations → results)
TempObs -->|hasResult| ResultTemp
WindObs -->|hasResult| ResultWind
LichtObs -->|hasResult| ResultLicht
RegenObs -->|hasResult| ResultRegen
AfwObs -->|hasResult| ResultAfw
RaamAct -->|hasResult| ResultRaam

%% Derivation-relaties
AfwObs -->|prov:used| ResultTemp
RaamAct -->|prov:used| ResultAfw
RaamAct -->|prov:used| ResultWind
RaamAct -->|prov:used| ResultLicht
RaamAct -->|prov:used| ResultRegen

%% Result → variable
ResultTemp -->|correspondsToVariable| VarTemp
ResultWind -->|correspondsToVariable| VarWind
ResultLicht -->|correspondsToVariable| VarLicht
ResultRegen -->|correspondsToVariable| VarRegen
ResultAfw -->|correspondsToVariable| VarAfw
ResultRaam -->|correspondsToVariable| VarRaamStand
